I added the story of
lymphatics and tonsils

00:28:13.590 --> 00:28:15.570 align:middle line:84%
because there's been
a misunderstanding

00:28:15.570 --> 00:28:18.360 align:middle line:84%
of the nature of how
we actually provide

00:28:18.360 --> 00:28:21.000 align:middle line:90%
